<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nitlak nak pinah, Maw zinglei dawh cu, Khamhtu he vancung kan len
 tikah, Lei rian har dih i, Maw ceunak sunglawi, Nitlak nak pin le, caan
 dongh tikah.

[V2]
 Nitlak nak pinah, Minmei a um lo, Thlichia tihnak zong a um ti lo, Maw
 lawmhnak caantha, Ceunak dong loin, Nitlak nak pin cu, zungzal lawmhnak.

[V3]
 Nitlak nak pinah, Kan Pa inn tiang in, Dawtnak kutnem nih a ka hruai
 lai, A bia thlum bik le, Kan um tinak cu, Khi tiva ral ah, kan ro a si.

[V4]
 Nitlak nak pinah kan i tong than lai, A kal cia kan hawi dawtmi hna
 he, Khika ramnuam ah then a um ti lo, Nitlak nak pinah kan i din lai.</lyrics>
<title>NITLAKNAK PINAH CH437</title>
<hymn_number>437</hymn_number>
</song>